NAME
	query_remote_port - give the remote tcp port of the player 

SYNOPSIS
	int query_remote_port(void|object player)

DESCRIPTION
    Gives the remote port of an interactive object.
    If the object is not interactive 0 will be returned.
	
	The number returned is in the range 0 - 65536.

NOTES
	The function valid_query_ip_number_name() is called in
	"/secure/master" to allow filtering of the results based on caller.

SEE ALSO
	query_ip_number, query_ip_name

